**THE TEST CASES WERE PERFORMED USING CODELESS TESTING TOOL (TESTIM)
(Chrome | Windows 10 | 1024 X 680)


##TEST CASE 1 Positive Test Case (Valid Credentials)
    **Steps:
Navigate to URL:
Action: Navigate to https://www.saucedemo.com/.
Enter Username:
Action: Input standard_user into the username field (#user-name).
Enter Password:
Action: Input secret_sauce into the password field (#password).
Click Login Button:
Action: Click the login button (#login-button).
Validate Successful Login:
Assertion: Verify that the URL contains inventory.html or that an element (e.g., #inventory_container) is visible. 

**Link to testim https://app.testim.io/#/project/UfyRGUDz9AzQFYIe7Vic/branch/master/test/0ZsfhAkTFBqoowcn?result-id=aa1Yrf9I6lHNTy0L

##TEST CASE 2  Negative Test Case (Invalid Credentials)
     **Steps:
Navigate to URL:
Action: Navigate to https://www.saucedemo.com/.
Enter Invalid Username:
Action: Input invalid_user into the username field (#user-name).
Enter Invalid Password:
Action: Input invalid_password into the password field (#password).
Click Login Button:
Action: Click the login button (#login-button).
Validate Error Message:
Assertion: Verify that the error message Epic sadface: Username and password do not match is displayed in the error container (.error-message-container).

**Link to testim https://app.testim.io/#/project/UfyRGUDz9AzQFYIe7Vic/branch/master/test/JjFlbB04T3FFOkJM?result-id=GZmPMxpQUZOZtvP1

##TEST CASE 3  Negative Test Case (Empty Fields)
   **Steps:
Navigate to URL:
Action: Navigate to https://www.saucedemo.com/.
Leave Fields Blank:
Action: Do not enter any text into the username or password fields.
Click Login Button:
Action: Click the login button (#login-button).
Validate Error Message:
Assertion: Verify that the error message Epic sadface: Username is required is displayed in the error container (.error-message-container).

**Link to testim https://app.testim.io/#/project/UfyRGUDz9AzQFYIe7Vic/branch/master/test/XvS6krUsH01T0x2r
